              <th class="font-display text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-ink py-4 pr-4">Spiral Conveyor</th>
              <th class="font-display text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-ink py-4 pr-4">VRC (Reciprocating)</th>
              <th class="font-display text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-ink py-4">Incline Belt Conveyor</th>
            </tr>
